snippet.title: STORY OF SEASONS: A Wonderful Life | Multiplatform trailer
snippet.description:
Put down roots on your new farm in the peaceful town of Forgotten Valley, and tell your own generation-spanning tale in STORY OF SEASONS: A Wonderful Life, coming to Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S and Steam in Summer 2023.

Find out more on: 
Web: https://marvelousgames.com/
Twitter: http://twitter.com/storyofseasons
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/marvelouseurope
Instagram: http://instagram.com/marvelouseurope
